"{\"uid\": \"perthnow.com.au-sport-olympics-olympic-games-2024-french-pole-vaulter-anthony-ammirati-goes-rival-after-buldge-touches-bar-c-15585282\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Get the FREE App  Get the FREE App  A French pole vaulter has gone viral after his Olympic dream ended when his crotch hit the bar at the Paris Games overnight.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 44, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.6892667655024464, \"rank\": 0.446611400407579, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anthony Ammirati was on his third attempt to clear the 5.70m height, with eagle-eyed social media users spotting exactly which part of his body had knocked him out of contention.\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 340, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Footage of the 22-year-old's attempt quickly went viral on X (formerly Twitter) with more than nine million views.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you'd like to view this content, please adjust yourCookie Settings.\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To find out more about how we use cookies, please see ourCookie Guide.\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"oh he brought that baguette to the games,\\\" one user wrote.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, you win some you lose some,\\\" another said.\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"More comments on X included: \\\"Suffering from success, \\\"Loses vault.\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wins internet\\\" and \\\"Stiff competition.\\\"\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While social media relentlessly mocked the Frenchman, Ammirati w